parameters.name: CurrentPage
parameters.description: The number of the page to return. Default value: **1**.

parameters.name: Dealed
parameters.description:
Specifies whether the event on web tamper proofing is handled. Valid values:

*   **n**: The event on web tamper proofing is handled.
*   **y**: The event on web tamper proofing is not handled.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page. Default value: **10**.

parameters.name: Remark
parameters.description:
The name of the asset.

> You can call the [DescribeCloudCenterInstances](~~DescribeCloudCenterInstances~~) operation to query the names of assets.

parameters.name: TsBegin
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to query. The value is a UNIX timestamp.

parameters.name: TsEnd
parameters.description: The end of the time range to query. The value is a UNIX timestamp.
